⁣
A high conversion rate is an indication of success with your marketing strategy. 📈⁣
⁣
This showcases the value of your products or services to your audience so they can easily find and learn about them. 🤓⁣
⁣
❗️Most brand owners in any niche having trouble scaling aren’t paying attention to this❗️⁣
⁣
Be aware of the necessary steps that your numbers present to you so you can make adjustments that will give you the knowledge to grow your brand. ⁣
⁣
Life fact: People are out here winning with the same formula, you just need to make sure you're  following the right one. 💯⁣
⁣
📲 If you guys need help scaling your brand hit the link in my bio to apply to work with us.⁣
⁣
If you’re a good fit we can get on a call and see how we can help you with your next powerhouse brand. 👊🏼

node.text:
No one is going to hand you a good life.

👉You have to want a good life for yourself, and have a real and active plan on how you intend to attain it.

➕ Do you have a plan?

➕ Do you have a goal?

🤔 Are you doing the things that are required to make sure you actually reach the things that you seek?

❌ If you are not really planning then you are planning to fail.

➡️ "Dreams without goals are just that….dreams."

You have to Aspire to Make a Difference in order to really create a change in your life, or anyone else's.

It doesn’t matter what the dream is, whether it's to be super fit, super famous, or in my case and many of my peers a super successful entrepreneur.

➡️ All of those things take goals, and effort.

Make sure you have both of those things, and also like minded people around you to help you stay the course and remain motivated.

🎯 If you have a dream of being a successful business owner and you would like to take that dream and turn it into a goal instead of just a dream by starting your own business….

Or if you're already a business owner and you're looking for help scaling your business, or just want help getting the process started…..

✅ DM me or Comment "SAVAGE" down below.

Let's get you set up with the right team of people so we can turn that DREAM into a GOAL.

Let's set up a call guys!!! 📞📞📞

node.text:
Dreams are for everyone.

👉 Goals are for people who are daring enough to turn their dreams into them, and go after them.

🌍 This world is quick to pass its judgement on you, that’s because people are so quick to cast their own fears on to other people.

➡️ The people that are able to rise above all of that type of energy, and push through for the things that they want are the only ones that are capable of ever seeing their dreams, and goals come into fruition.

I think this reality couldn't be more true than how true it is for an entrepreneur.

It seems like the entire process of becoming your own self employed boss is looked down upon until the moment people see you're actually capable of making it happen…..

You actually knew what you wanted for yourself, and made it your reality.

🖨 So the way I see it, if people are going to hate on you anyways no matter what you do, you might as well really give them something to hate about right?

🎯 With that being said if you're looking to turn your dreams of being a successful business owner into a real goal or….

If you're already a business owner and you're looking for help scaling your business, or just want help getting the process started…..

✅ DM me or Comment "SAVAGE" down below.

Time to give your hater something to really hate about..…

Let's set up a call guys!!!📞📞📞

node.text:
Believing that you can achieve is the first step to actually doing just that.
 
👉 We live in a society filled with people who are leading or following; this is just facts.
 
🤔 Now the thing about this statement is that a lot of the time when someone decides they no longer want to be a follower  they want to lead……
 
Some of the other followers don’t like that and they want to try to keep that person mentally trap like them. 🤯🤯🤯
 
➡️ This type of energy isn't just a one time situation either this is pretty much the everyday reality of the dreamer, the entrepreneur…….whatever you want to label yourself as.
 
😠 My point you've probably already felt this situation a million times over….
 
We all have, and that probably wont ever stop no matter what heights you may reach. 🤷‍♂️🤷‍♂️🤷‍♂️
 
They'll always be someone trying to tell you what you're capable of.
 
You have to be so sure of what's right for you that no amount of negative energy can make you fold on your beliefs about what you have to bring to the table.
 
You only have to be right once….and once you prove it you just have to keep showing people that you always were and will be for betting on yourself.
 
🎯 Believe in your process and what you have to offer.
 
If you want to start taking the steps towards your success or calling or…..
 
If you're looking for help scaling your  business, or just want help getting started…..

node.text:
Optimizing Your Ad Spend⁣
⁣
👉 In this day and age if your doing your business online; chances are any ad ideas or marketing techniques that you might want to try have already been done.⁣
⁣
Lets just be honest with ourselves, doesn't matter how original you think you are....someone's probably already thought of it and done it too.⁣ 🤷‍♂️🤷‍♂️🤷‍♂️
⁣
➡️ That reality can be a frustrating one to soak in but that's ok its not the end of the world, and that can also work in your favor sometimes.⁣
⁣
Now my point for saying this at all is that with a market that is so oversaturated with the same ideas, and same type of content on the same platform......FACEBOOK.⁣
⁣
How do you stand out?⁣ ⬅️
⁣
What is the best way to make sure your products get seen, and you're getting a nice return on your AD Spend?⁣ 👀👀👀
⁣
🎯 We need to be outsourcing our ADS to other platform that can offer us more opportunity for retargeting clientele.⁣ 
⁣
In this video today Malby checks in to give you the perfect play by play on how to further your ADS success through other platforms.⁣
⁣
There's a million different ways to make a million you guys. Just got to find one!⁣ 💵
⁣
Drop two 💯💯 in the comments if you agree! ⁣
⁣

👉 In business knowing your strengths and weaknesses is prolly one of the most important things for your success.⁣
⁣
It can honestly be detrimental to you if you're not aware of them. There could be opportunities your missing because you're not using your strengths to make them happen; or your weaknesses could be the very reason they fall through. ⁣
⁣
➡️ Knowing yourself is key in every aspect. I can honestly say my self awareness, and confidence in how well I know what I have to offer in a situation is the reason why I've attained many of the things , and moments that have made me who I am today.⁣
⁣
Know yourself enough to grow yourself that's the best advice that I could give anyone.⁣ 🌱🌱🌱
⁣
If you guys need help finding your strengths so you can scale your business online, or just want to start trying....⁣💸💸💸

node.text:
Online Courses As a Bolt On Business⁣
⁣
👉 If you're an entrepreneur in this day and age your business in someway shape, or form should be online. ⁣
⁣
With almost everyone taking their business to the online format its easy to blend in with the masses. Without the proper marketing your brand can easily go unnoticed, and this is just one of the potential issues that could hinder your growth, or exposure.⁣
⁣ ❌ Especially if you're trying to grow your business by running ads, or sales through places like Facebook.⁣
⁣
Now lets say you're lucky enough to have a pretty solid understanding of how to market your business online, you still could be missing another key element of growing your brand.⁣ 🔑🔑🔑
⁣
➡️ Knowledge is power, and we live in an age where knowledge is just one click way.⁣
⁣
Why not literally profit off your knowledge, by being that one click away.⁣ ⁣
ONLINE COURSES...⁣💲💲💲

node.text:
Ideation is one of the most crucial processes to engage in any initiative you take on. 

It's important that you take the time to figure out what works and what doesn't work. This requires you to really get down to it, empathize with others, and do your research to really understand the frustrations or needs of your users. You have to be able to define what the problem is that customers are experiencing, and then from there, generate new ideas on how your product or service will actually target this issue that other companies in the marketplace have missed. 

Figure out where the gap is and what you will do better to close it. Give yourself and your team the space to brainstorm and think creatively on how to apply different methods to design your solution. 

Involve the human experience in every step of your problem-solving process. 

-⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣

"Shift your perspective to embrace difficult trials as personal challenges to grow. Face the struggle head on to come out of it unharmed. 

Don't let setbacks discourage you. Turn them into something beautiful. There's always something to learn when you get knocked down. The hardships we face in life aren't for nothing, and they won't break you if you don't let them. Hardships build character, humble you, and make you stronger and more resilient to whatever comes next in your life. 

Playing victim when bad things happen to you won't do you any good. You gotta discipline your mind to find the good in bad situations. Defining difficult events as experiences will make all the difference in the future you create for yourself.

node.text:
Are you letting your fears hold you back?⁣
⁣
When you don't want to do something, ask yourself WHY.⁣
⁣
Most of the time, the reason people procrastinate is FEAR. They think they won't be able to achieve their goals. So how do you cure this procrastination? How do you start?⁣
⁣
It's really simple.⁣
⁣
You just have to take ACTION! ⁣
⁣
Action cures fear. ⁣
⁣
⁣
Fear only lives in our minds.⁣
⁣
Once you build confidence from taking action, you are more likely to continue with a task until you finish it.⁣
⁣
If you want to kill fear, then take ACTION!⁣
⁣
Tag someone who needs to see this. 👇⁣
⁣

node.text:
In business, determination is everything. If you're determined, there's almost nothing that can stop you. ⁣
⁣
However, if you lack determination, you may be easily discouraged or even worse - give up. ⁣
⁣
What can help you stay determined and on track? Keep good habits.⁣
⁣
It's not the big steps that take you to your desired goal but the small things you do consistently every day.⁣
⁣
So think of the habits necessary for you to achieve your financial, personal, and emotional goals. ⁣
⁣
